### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### models.http — Model Catalog Contract (ADR-040)
### Validates the gateway model discovery endpoints respond correctly.
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Authenticate
# @name login
POST {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{$dotenv ADMIN_EMAIL}}",
  "password": "{{$dotenv ADMIN_PASSWORD}}"
}

?? status == 200

###

### List Supported Models
# @name listSupportedModels
GET {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/models/supported
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}

?? status == 200

###

### List All Providers
# @name listProviders
GET {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/models/providers
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}

?? status == 200

###

### List Model Catalog
# @name listModelCatalog
GET {{$dotenv GATEWAY_TARGET_URL}}/api/v1/models/catalog
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.token}}

?? status == 200


